records.addlTxt:
Sentence is withheld and the defendant is placed on probation to DOC for two (2) years.
Conditions of probation:
1)	AODA assessment and follow through;
2)	Assessment, treatment, counseling as recommended by the Department's assessment process;
3)	Submit to random urine screens and pay for same;
4)	Maintain absolute sobriety;
5)	Maintain fulltime employment, schooling, treatment, work search or combination;
6)	Contact with no assaultive contact with C.P.
7)	Pay court costs;
8)	pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC;
9)	provide DNA sample.
Minutes.
